description: There's no better way to start your day than with a delicious meal from the Brunch Truck! The delicious dishes of Square Cafe combined with the great flavor and years of dedication from Uncle Charley's Sausage is sure to be an eating experience you won't forget. If you're eager to experience a real cafe on wheels, don't miss out on this terrific truck's amazing menu today!
name: Uncle Charley’s + Square Cafe Brunch Truck
